<p>
  <%= receipt.date.strftime("%B %-d, %Y") %>
</p>

<p>
  <%= receipt.donor_full_name %>

  <% if receipt.donor_address.present? %>
    <br /><%= receipt.donor_address %>
  <% end %>

  <% if receipt.donor_email.present? %>
    <br/><%= receipt.donor_email %>
  <% end %>
</p>

<p>
  RE: Your Thank You and Tax Receipt
</p>

<p>
  Dear <%= receipt.donor_first_name %>,
</p>

<p>
  Thank you for your commitment to The Grateful Garment Project's mission to
  ensure that all sexual assault victims who cross the threshold of SART
  facilities or who go through the examination process are provided with
  whatever new clothing, toiletry and snack items they may require to reduce any
  additional impact on their being.
</p>

<p>
  We are delighted to have you as part of our caring family. The donation you
  made of <%= receipt.donations_list %> will help us provide the most humane
  care possible.  The Grateful Garment Project is a 501(c)(3) not-for-profit
  organization.  Our Tax ID Number is <%= Rails.application.config.tax_id %>. In
  accordance with Internal Revenue Code 6115, we hereby state your donation is
  tax deductible.
</p>

<p>
  The entire The Grateful Garment Project family, of which you are a vital part,
  joins me in thanking you for your support.  Please feel free to call us at
  <%= Rails.application.config.contact_phone_formatted %> to share your comments
  or suggestions.
</p>

<p>
  Gratefully yours,<br />
  Lisa J. Blanchard<br />
  Executive Director
</p>

<p>
  <%= Rails.application.config.contact_street_address_line %>, <%= Rails.application.config.contact_city_line %><br />
  <%= Rails.application.config.contact_phone_formatted %> - <%= Rails.application.config.contact_email %>
</p>
